In this project, program is stored in two different files with declaration in the "base.h" header file.

The Main function of the program is stored in the assg1.cpp
The Classes , its member variables and the functions have been written in classes.cpp file.

To Execute the program , open the directory in the Ubuntu Terminal and execute the following commands.
1. make compile
	This command will command will compile the program.
2. make run
	This command will run the same program in the shell from which this process was called. 